data.description: Beautiful 5-bedroom, 4 full bath home in a sought-after neighborhood, 'Sentinel Walk'. This property is a 'must see'. One homeowner, who spent a lot of time traveling, so house is like new. There is a guest room on the main floor with a full bath adjacent to the room. Separate living and dining rooms, along with a beautiful open kitchen and family room. Granite counter tops, stainless steal appliances. 10 ft ceilings, a 2-story entry foyer, as well as the family room. Upstairs the oversized Master Suite includes a huge 5 piece bath, and 2 large his and her walk in closets. 2 additional bedrooms have their own on-suites and 2 bedrooms share a jack and jill bathroom. There is space for everyone in this home. The laundry room is also upstairs for convenience. Tons of closet space, 2 car garage. Home sits on a half-acre lot with a large open backyard. This home won't stay on the market long. Be ready to visit and make this your new "Home".
